data.description: This beauty needs a little elbow grease to restore the old world bungalow charm and bring it back to its glory. Believed to have hardwood under carpets in main living areas and bedrooms, original windows (some need replaced), Roof 2009 HVAC 2005 1 car detached garage with a ramp to the back deck and back entry of home, shed, fenced in yard, updated kitchen (all appliances stay), dining room. Bathroom needs a vanity and shower/tub has a cutout to allow handicap accessibility. Selling AS IS. Is an estate sale.
